{"tid":1613600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以唔好再淨係戴個口罩就去Set路障，又幫手搬嘢","createTime":"2019-10-02T14:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T13:31:11.000Z","uid":23094,"like":132,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"a1b477a0a39f626097d965d21fb02fd5efca925f","tid":1613600,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:49:36.000Z","msg":"其實口罩遮唔到幾多㗎喳<br />\n你起碼都戴返頂帽吖<br />\n仲有好多人冇著黑衫黑衫<br />\n其實喺鏡頭下係好撚搶眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你曾經淨係戴個口罩，帽都唔戴<br />\n又或者冇著到全黑，著平時自己去街衫<br />\n就走去幫手搬嘢，幫手Set路障<br />\n甚至整魔法，甚至出魔法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我求下你<br />\n即刻掉哂發夢著過嘅衫，以後唔好再著<br />\n仲有即刻去改髮型，染髮<br />\n總之要搞到呀媽都唔認得</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算唔係連登<br />\nTelegram嘅612 Reminder同Scott都已經講過無數次<br />\n已經4個月㗎喇<br />\n唔好再要人提呢啲嘢好冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知唔係個個手足都上連登<br />\n求下大家可唔可以幫手Share去其他社交平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1aa4213a7601e0757407b5bcc5380d58fc10dc","tid":1613600,"uid":23094,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:50:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有好多人冇著黑衫黑*褲*</span>"},{"pid":"d79b33badc2bed8304bb8874cb40d3a5d504c225","tid":1613600,"uid":23094,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"你啲衫褲好撚柒呀<br />\n好心就掉鳩哂佢，以後咪撚著啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有你個頭都好撚柒呀<br />\n好心就轉下髮型，學下人染髮啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ec70578